steps.name: $("By.xpath: //a[@href='/' and contains(@style, 'orange')]") should have(attribute style="color: orange;")
$("#header/By.xpath: .//ul[@class='nav navbar-nav']//a[normalize-space(text())='Signup / Login']") should not have([attribute disabled, 30 s.])
$("#header/By.xpath: .//ul[@class='nav navbar-nav']//a[normalize-space(text())='Signup / Login']") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
input user name Dr. Shannon Mueller
$(".signup-form/button") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //input[@value='Mr']") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$("#name") should not be([empty: attribute value="" and exact text "", 30 s.])
$("#email") should not be([empty: attribute value="" and exact text "", 30 s.])
